    LLMISGW -->|AuthPolicy| LLMISPods
    NotebookGW -->|kube-rbac-proxy| Notebooks
    ModelRegGW -->|kube-rbac-proxy| ModelRegInst
    MLflowGW -->|K8s RBAC| MLflowInst
    FeastGW -->|OIDC| FeastInst
    RayDashGW -->|OAuth proxy| RayCluster
    MaaSGW -->|Authorino| MaaSPods

