    KueueCtrl -->|admission| RayCluster
    CodeFlareCtrl -->|manages| RayCluster
    KubeRayCtrl -->|manages| RayCluster
    TrainingCtrl -->|manages training| UserNS
    TrustyAICtrl -->|auto-config| GuardrailsPods
    ModelRegOpCtrl -->|deploys| ModelRegInst
    MLflowOpCtrl -->|deploys| MLflowInst
    FeastOpCtrl -->|deploys| FeastInst
    ModelMeshCtrl -->|deploys| ModelMeshPods

    %% Dashboard integrations
    Dashboard -->|REST| DSPInstance
    Dashboard -->|REST/gRPC| ModelRegInst

    %% Monitoring
    Monitoring -.->|scrapes metrics| AppNS

    %% Egress
    ISPods -->|model download<br/>HTTPS| S3
    LLMISPods -->|model download<br/>HTTPS| S3
    DSPInstance -->|artifacts<br/>HTTPS| S3
    ModelRegInst -->|metadata| DB
    MLflowInst -->|experiments| DB
    MLflowInst -->|artifacts| S3
    Notebooks -->|data| S3
    ModelMeshPods -->|model download| S3
    OdhModelCtrl -->|NIM catalog| NIM

    %% Hidden K8s API node
    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SA tokens"]

